{"tid":467021,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"因為一句說話俾人炒左","createTime":"2017-11-13T06:22:35.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-14T02:25:10.000Z","uid":36310,"like":1658,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":60,"replies":[{"pid":"1a448b02d8e53d8112fd93dd9b0fc2d844429f59","tid":467021,"uid":36310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T06:22:35.000Z","msg":"話說我老闆個口頭禪就係 &quot;no excuse&quot;<br />\n一做錯野同佢解釋返都會話 &quot;no excuse&quot;<br />\n<br />\n咁今日星期一幾個dept開例會啦<br />\n我就坐係前面 今日噴左支味比較濃嘅香水<br />\n一坐低準備開會老闆就係咁打乞嚏<br />\n佢就即刻講:excuse me<br />\n我就潛意識咁講句<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">&quot;no excuse&quot;</span></span><br />\n就係依句說句搞到失業<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3aa6026cfe560d22fe88664a02945d1b1bde3871","tid":467021,"uid":85659,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T06:23:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9af20bde99c3157f2955fb7bf4c3047fc859fce1","tid":467021,"uid":8302,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T06:24:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e01e7336084ae92a2d0de43cdef28ca99ef954b","tid":467021,"uid":1139,"like":174,"dislike":1,"score":173,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T06:24:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8322536b81de1a12cb6fbcb9fe9ae3b13e2885e1","tid":467021,"uid":23629,"like":103,"dislike":1,"score":102,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T06:24:31.000Z","msg":"你老闆仲小氣過方丈"},{"pid":"a144d81e6c24f9d4455151647d061c8064c59cfb","tid":467021,"uid":35